{"tid":1493890,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"已經諗好經濟差避免食草既plan","createTime":"2019-08-21T12:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T12:56:54.000Z","uid":113626,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"42922a18ed1f9f8371b83f1939611c27cdeb9bf9","tid":1493890,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:08:53.000Z","msg":"經濟差就緊係求生存, 如果萬一失業, 就算洗幾少錢都好, 根本連買野食都係消耗緊資本 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左野食日用品, 基本上其他最好乜都唔好買<br />\n1. 朝早食麥片算, 應該食到好飽除返開都係幾蚊<br />\n2. 中午夜晚走去果d咩唐記包點買個飯+野飲, 應該都係30$附近<br />\n30+30+幾$=70$就捱到一日, 一個月都係2100$, 當交埋上網費電話費日用品果d都係3000$以下<br />\n如果要比家用, 你失業屋企人都應該要體諒你, 比3000$當極限算第時搵到工先再比多d<br />\n最重要都係盡快搵返份工過正常生活  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e642a8e480be56bbd6afc2d857be191e5a97f2","tid":1493890,"uid":91813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:10:07.000Z","msg":"唔我而家都冇食得咁豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ea613ca94447445fc90f56c3c7644c2baefbab","tid":1493890,"uid":22337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:11:18.000Z","msg":"你而家入返幾箱牛餐肉,之後個d野唔洗講啦"},{"pid":"7cdbf74bf2c5569257064ed19482b7baa02fe2f5","tid":1493890,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d9ea613ca94447445fc90f56c3c7644c2baefbab","tid":1493890,"uid":22337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:11:18.000Z","msg":"你而家入返幾箱牛餐肉,之後個d野唔洗講啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:14:55.000Z","msg":"太過想當然了"},{"pid":"34e473f21cd201028f87c1d1079200f98aa3423e","tid":1493890,"uid":41524,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T12:17:38.000Z","msg":"咁豪!?!?!<br />\n我諗住幾十蚊一袋8KG米食一個月<br />\n餐餐淨白飯"},{"pid":"40866fcb1430d852704eb3f2e859853499e195ff","tid":1493890,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34e473f21cd201028f87c1d1079200f98aa3423e","tid":1493890,"uid":41524,"like":6,"disli